AMU Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for Senior Resident Post
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 08, 2025, 12:07 IST
 Aligarh Muslim University
 1 Jobs |  Posted On : 08-Aug-2025 |  Uttar Pradesh |  Salary : 56,100 to 56,100




FOLLOW

Aligarh Muslim University (AMU) has released its official notification for the recruitment of Senior Resident positions for the year 2025. Those candidates who have qualified in the MD/ MS, DNB can apply for the AMU Recruitment 2025. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible aspirants can apply online through the website on or before the last date of application. For more details, visit the official website.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Uttar Pradesh.

AMU Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Senior Resident 	01	MD/ MS, DNB

Age limit for the AMU Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 35 years

Selection Process for the AMU Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the AMU Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 56,100 /-per month.

Application fee for the AMU Recruitment 2025

There is no application fee.
How to Apply for the AMU Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Senior Resident Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Click on the Apply Online link.
Register with your email and password.
Download the application form.
Fill out the application form without any mistakes.
Then, send the application form along with the relevant documents to the address given below.

Address

Office of Dean, J.N. Medical College, Faculty of Medicine, Aligarh Muslim University, Aligarh 202002.

Important Dates

Starting Date of Application	07-08-2025
Last Date of Application	14-08-2025
